---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy | Rosemary Berkon">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: 17 February 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-8">
      <p>
        Your privacy matters. This policy explains what personal information I collect, why I collect it, and how it is used when you interact with this website or book training sessions.
      </p>
      <p>
        I operate as an independent voice and accent coach based in the United Kingdom. For the purposes of data protection law, I am the &ldquo;data controller&rdquo; of the personal data you provide.
      </p>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3">1. What Information I Collect</h2>
        <p>I may collect the following information:</p>
        <p class="font-medium mt-3">Contact information</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Name</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Social media handle (if you contact me via DM)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="font-medium mt-3">Booking information</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Course or session purchased</li>
          <li>Payment confirmation (via Stripe &mdash; I do not see or store card details)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="font-medium mt-3">Communication</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Emails you send me</li>
          <li>Messages relating to coaching or training</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="font-medium mt-3">Technical data</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Basic website analytics, such as page visits and general location (country level only)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3">2. How Your Information Is Used</h2>
        <p>Your information is used only to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li>Provide the training or service you booked</li>
          <li>Send booking confirmations and course information</li>
          <li>Respond to enquiries</li>
          <li>Send newsletters or updates (only if you have opted in)</li>
          <li>Improve course delivery and website experience</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">I do not sell or share your data for advertising.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3">3. Payments</h2>
        <p>Payments are processed securely through Stripe. I do not store or have access to your full payment details. Stripe processes data according to its own privacy policy.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3">4. Email Communications</h2>
        <p>If you subscribe to updates, your email address is stored in my mailing system (MailerLite). You can unsubscribe at any time using the link at the bottom of any email.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">Course-related emails (such as booking confirmations or session details) will still be sent where necessary to deliver a service you have purchased.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3">5. Legal Basis for Processing (UK GDPR)</h2>
        <p>I process your data under the following lawful bases:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Contract</strong> &mdash; to provide the training you have booked</li>
          <li><strong>Legitimate interest</strong> &mdash; to communicate regarding enquiries</li>
          <li><strong>Consent</strong> &mdash; for newsletters and marketing emails</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3">6. How Long Your Data Is Kept</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Booking records: up to 6 years (for accounting purposes)</li>
          <li>Emails: until you unsubscribe or request deletion</li>
          <li>Enquiries that do not result in booking: periodically deleted</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3">7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li>Access your data</li>
          <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent</li>
          <li>Lodge a complaint with the ICO (Information Commissioner&rsquo;s Office)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">To exercise any of these rights, email: <a href="mailto:rosemary.berkon@gmail.com" class="text-teal underline">rosemary.berkon@gmail.com</a></p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3">8. Cookies</h2>
        <p>This website may use basic cookies for functionality and analytics. You can disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3">9. Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this policy or how your data is used, contact:</p>
        <p class="mt-3">Rosemary Berkon Voice<br />Email: <a href="mailto:rosemary.berkon@gmail.com" class="text-teal underline">rosemary.berkon@gmail.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
